org.apache.flink.streaming.api.operators

接口 OneInputStreamOperator<IN,OUT>

  • 类型参数:
    IN - The input type of the operator
    OUT - The output type of the operator
    所有超级接口:
    Serializable, StreamOperator<OUT>
    所有已知实现类:
    AbstractAlignedProcessingTimeWindowOperator, AccumulatingProcessingTimeWindowOperator, AggregatingProcessingTimeWindowOperator, ContinuousFileReaderOperator, EvictingWindowOperator, ExtractTimestampsOperator, GenericWriteAheadSink, StreamCounter, StreamFilter, StreamFlatMap, StreamGroupedFold, StreamGroupedReduce, StreamMap, StreamProject, StreamSink, TimestampsAndPeriodicWatermarksOperator, TimestampsAndPunctuatedWatermarksOperator, WindowOperator

    @PublicEvolving
public interface OneInputStreamOperator<IN,OUT>
extends StreamOperator<OUT>
    Interface for stream operators with one input. Use AbstractStreamOperator as a base class if you want to implement a custom operator.
